534
00:18:53,298 --> 00:18:56,217
IT WAS AN ORDINARY
HIGH SCHOOL STUDENT'S ROOM

535
00:18:56,218 --> 00:18:59,428
NOW, IT'S COVERED
IN A MYSTERIOUS BLACK FLUID

536
00:18:59,429 --> 00:19:01,430
