539
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:12,358
- Hang on.
- Is something left?

540
00:19:12,359 --> 00:19:13,609
It's even in the photo.

541
00:19:13,610 --> 00:19:14,527
What is that?

542
00:19:14,528 --> 00:19:16,237
- Look at this.
- It's affected the photo.

543
00:19:16,238 --> 00:19:17,405
BLACK FLUID ON JUST DEOK-U'S FACE

544
00:19:17,406 --> 00:19:19,157
That's so chilling.

545
00:19:19,158 --> 00:19:21,076
The fluid takes over every aspect of them?

546
00:19:21,577 --> 00:19:23,244
He looks like Chucky or a <i>jiangshi.</i>

547
00:19:23,245 --> 00:19:25,872
Could it be a kind of Halloween disguise?

548
00:19:25,873 --> 00:19:28,040
- It's all over the walls.
- Right?

549
00:19:28,041 --> 00:19:28,876
Why is that?

550
00:19:29,459 --> 00:19:30,793
Should we turn on his laptop?

551
00:19:30,794 --> 00:19:31,753
- Yes.
- Yes.

552
00:19:32,629 --> 00:19:34,839
OPENING THE LAPTOP ON THE DESK

553
