558
00:19:44,766 --> 00:19:46,100
"I am"?

559
00:19:46,101 --> 00:19:47,018
I am…

560
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:48,102
Oh Deok.

561
00:19:48,103 --> 00:19:49,145
I am…

562
00:19:49,146 --> 00:19:51,230
