566
00:19:58,906 --> 00:20:00,865
- He was 17 years old.
- Oh Deok-u.

567
00:20:00,866 --> 00:20:01,782
He was a student.

568
00:20:01,783 --> 00:20:04,160
Try "student," Karina.

569
00:20:04,161 --> 00:20:07,330
ENTERING "STUDENT"

570
00:20:07,331 --> 00:20:08,247
WRONG PASSWORD

571
00:20:08,248 --> 00:20:09,791
What could it be?

572
00:20:10,584 --> 00:20:12,085
Or maybe…

573
00:20:18,967 --> 00:20:21,803
