599
00:21:20,404 --> 00:21:21,822
- I'll scroll to the very top.
- Okay.

600
00:21:23,365 --> 00:21:25,408
"You got a new phone
during admissions season?"

601
00:21:25,409 --> 00:21:29,412
"King MS is coming
to Baeksudam on the 29th."

602
00:21:29,413 --> 00:21:30,622
King MS?

603
00:21:32,582 --> 00:21:33,666
"So, he agreed to meet."

604
00:21:33,667 --> 00:21:35,501
"I said I'd give them the garden key."

605
00:21:35,502 --> 00:21:36,628
The garden key?

606
00:21:37,337 --> 00:21:39,672
"I stole the key from I-jang's house."

607
00:21:39,673 --> 00:21:41,967
"He was in charge of Baeksudam Garden."

608
00:21:42,592 --> 00:21:43,552
Hang on.

609
00:21:44,469 --> 00:21:46,847
- "How did you get in his house?"
- Didn't someone die there?

610
00:21:47,472 --> 00:21:49,766
"He keeps his key under the jar stand."

611
00:21:50,767 --> 00:21:52,101
They had arranged

612
00:21:52,102 --> 00:21:56,314
to meet someone and give them a key.

613
00:21:56,315 --> 00:21:58,984
They seemed to be up to something risky.

614
00:21:59,568 --> 00:22:01,193
"Can you still not reach him?"

615
00:22:01,194 --> 00:22:02,236
"He won't read my messages."

616
00:22:02,237 --> 00:22:04,196
"Has something happened to him?"

617
00:22:04,197 --> 00:22:05,281
- Does that mean…
- Oh, look.

618
00:22:05,282 --> 00:22:07,367
He says, "Is the Prosperity Hall on fire?"

619
00:22:07,951 --> 00:22:10,077
The black fluid was found there too.

620
00:22:10,078 --> 00:22:14,040
"The black fluid found on the dead bodies

621
00:22:14,041 --> 00:22:18,044
matches the substance found

622
00:22:18,045 --> 00:22:20,588
in the burned-down
Village Prosperity Hall."

623
00:22:20,589 --> 00:22:21,756
- What?
- What?

624
00:22:21,757 --> 00:22:23,215
The black fluid was found there first.

625
00:22:23,216 --> 00:22:24,718
This chat is dated July 2nd.

626
00:22:25,761 --> 00:22:27,553
THE BAEKSUDAM FIRE IS MENTIONED
IN THE GROUP CHAT

627
00:22:27,554 --> 00:22:29,847
"Do you think he's up to no good?"

628
00:22:29,848 --> 00:22:30,890
