631
00:22:35,103 --> 00:22:37,480
"I heard I-jang is dead."

632
00:22:37,481 --> 00:22:38,857
"His wife is dead too."

633
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,359
"It can't be him, can it?"

634
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:43,652
- "I still can't reach him."
- Who is "him"?

635
00:22:43,653 --> 00:22:45,654
"Did he kill the village head?"

636
00:22:45,655 --> 00:22:46,698
"No way."

637
00:22:48,075 --> 00:22:50,451
